<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="light">
  <meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light">
  <title>Welcome to {{company}}</title>
  <style>
    /* Accessibility-focused styles */
    :root {
      color-scheme: light;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      background-color: #F8F9FA;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #FFFFFF;
    }
    
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #F2BF0F;
    }
    
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      height: auto;
    }
    
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    
    h1 {
      color: #333333;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    
    h2 {
      color: #333333;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0 15px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    
    p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #F2BF0F;
      color: #333333 !important;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 16px;
      border: 2px solid #F2BF0F;
    }
    
    .button:hover, .button:focus {
      background-color: #E0B00E;
      border-color: #333333;
      outline: 2px solid #333333;
    }
    
    .feature-list {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .feature-list li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666666;
      border-top: 1px solid #EEEEEE;
    }
    
    .footer a {
      color: #666666;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    .footer a:hover, .footer a:focus {
      color: #333333;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    .social-links {
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    
    .social-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 10px;
      text-decoration: underline;
      color: #666666;
    }
    
    @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        width: 100% !important;
        max-width: 100% !important;
      }
      
      .content {
        padding: 20px 15px !important;
      }
      
      .button {
        display: block !important;
        width: 100% !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container" role="main">
    <div class="header" role="banner">
      <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="{{company}} Logo" class="logo" width="150" height="50">
    </div>
    
    <div class="content" role="article" aria-label="Welcome message">
      <h1>Welcome to {{company}}!</h1>
      
      <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for joining {{company}}. We're excited to have you on board! Your account has been successfully created and is now ready to use.</p>
      
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button" role="button" aria-label="Go to Dashboard">Go to Dashboard</a>
      
      <h2>Getting Started</h2>
      
      <p>Here are a few things you can do with your new account:</p>
      
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Complete your profile to personalize your experience</li>
        <li>Explore our services and solutions</li>
        <li>Connect with other users and expand your network</li>
        <li>Check out our resources and learning materials</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help. Simply reply to this email or contact us through our support portal.</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for choosing {{company}}. We look forward to helping you achieve your goals!</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The {{company}} Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer" role="contentinfo">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{company}}. All rights reserved.</p>
      
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="{{socialLinks.twitter}}" class="social-link" aria-label="Follow us on Twitter">Twitter</a>
        <a href="{{socialLinks.facebook}}" class="social-link" aria-label="Follow us on Facebook">Facebook</a>
        <a href="{{socialLinks.linkedin}}" class="social-link" aria-label="Follow us on LinkedIn">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
      
      <p>
        <a href="{{privacyUrl}}" aria-label="View Privacy Policy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
        <a href="{{termsUrl}}" aria-label="View Terms of Service">Terms of Service</a> | 
        <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}" aria-label="Unsubscribe from emails">Unsubscribe</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
